          </p>
          <p style="font-size:16px;line-height:1.4;">Saudi Tabreed District Cooling Co., backed by the Public Investment Fund and Tabreed UAE, plans <a href="https://link.longandshort.com/ls-10-01-2025-wn2-4-explore-an-ipo" target="_blank">to explore an IPO</a>. Tabreed was valued at $250 million in 2022. It provides centralized cooling solutions for the scorching Middle East climate. This IPO is part of Saudi Arabia’s broader push to diversify its economy under Vision 2030. The Saudi market remains hot, with over $4 billion raised in IPOs last year.</p>
